 <PERSON> Barry </PERSON> <PERSON> Schweid </PERSON> has covered diplomacy for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> since the <PERSON> Kissinger </PERSON> era.
