 <PERSON> Strat </PERSON> <PERSON> Douthat </PERSON> is the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Southeast </ORGANIZATION> regional reporter, based in <LOCATION> Atlanta </LOCATION>.
</TEXT>
